4.3.2 Replication Instructions
Step-by-Step Replication Guide:
# 1. Environment Setup
git clone https://github.com/EFM-Framework/Economic-Fracture-Mechanics
cd Economic-Fracture-Mechanics
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Data Preparation
python src/data/download_public_data.py
python src/data/preprocessing/data_cleaning_pipeline.py

# 3. Mathematical Validation
python tests/test_dimensional_consistency.py
python tests/test_mathematical_derivations.py

# 4. Model Training and Validation
python src/statistical_models/train_efm_model.py --config config/baseline.yaml
python src/statistical_models/model_validation.py --test-period 2016-2024

# 5. Performance Evaluation
python src/evaluation/generate_performance_report.py
python src/visualization/create_validation_plots.py

# 6. Replication Verification
python tests/test_full_replication.py --tolerance 0.001
Expected Output:
Replication Test Results:
✓ Mathematical derivations verified
✓ Dimensional consistency confirmed  
✓ Performance metrics replicated within tolerance
✓ Statistical significance confirmed
✓ All unit tests passed

Final Validation Score: 100% (Complete Replication Achieved)
